Show HN: Webhooky – a simple webhook testing service
text:
I wanted to learn web development in cloud so came up with a simple service that lets anyone receive web traffic and analyze the payload. 
I tried other similar services but the payload logs expire after some time so it was tricky to share. 
This one is designed to keep these payloads for a long time. 
No account, no ads, experimental service. Feedback is welcome :)
